2015-1788 (La. 11/15/16)

STATE EX REL. Gregory JONES v. STATE of Louisiana No. 2015-KH-1788 Supreme Court of Louisiana. 11/15/2016 PER CURIAM:

| denied. Relator has failed to file an application for post-conviction relief which sets out specific claims of constitutional errors requiring the requested documentation for support. State ex rel. Bernard v. Cr.D.C., 94-2247, p. 1 (La. 4/28/95), 653 So.2d 1174, 1175.
